title: DPS-BEST OF- Sep 14, 2020
itunes:title: DPS-BEST OF- Sep 14, 2020
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, with week 1 of NFL action almost complete DP recaps all that went down. How much should we read into TB12's debut with the Bucs? We're joined by Rick Stroud, who covers the Bucs for the Tampa Times, former Bears pro bowl lineman Kyle Long and Browns beat writer Mary Kay Cabot. Plus, where will Houston's former Head Coach Mike D'Antoni land next?
